org.magnos.task
Class TaskListenerAdapter<R>

java.lang.Object
  org.magnos.task.TaskListenerAdapter<R>
Type Parameters:
R - The result type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
TaskListener<R>
public class TaskListenerAdapter<R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TaskListener<R>

An adapter which implements all TaskListener methods. This can be used to only listen to specific task events.

Example Usage

 Task t = new ...
 t.async(new TastListenerAdapter() {
        public void onTaskFinish(Task t) {
                // task has finished (success, error, timed out, cancelled)
        }
 });

Author:
Philip Diffenderfer
